Onion DNS Forward 
Idea behind ODNS is to be a DNSCurve forwarder with same functionality into an existing server, adding link-level public-key protection to DNS packets.
=================================

Developed Under Linux

DNSCurve
  http://dnscurve.org/out-implement.html

APIs
  C++ Socket pakage
  http://www.alhem.net/Sockets
 
  Cryptography library NaCL
  http://nacl.cr.yp.to/
  Install NaCl
  https://www.os3.nl/2008-2009/students/michiel_timmers/rp1

Compiling
   Scons to build projet 
   http://www.scons.org/

Implementation Ref
   http://github.com/agl/dnscurve/tree/master

This code is avaliable
   https://github.com/pahagon/odns/tree/master
